<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٩٦٣ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7150">يَعْقُوبُ بْنُ إِبْرَاهِيمَ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1611">أَبُو أُسَامَةَ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4195">عُبَيْدُ اللهِ، </a><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٩⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«كَانَ رَسُولُ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> وَأَبُو بَكْرٍ وَعُمَرُ <span class="special">﵄</span> يُصَلُّونَ الْعِيدَيْنِ قَبْلَ الْخُطْبَةِ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>